               <P>The Danish act on enforcement of procurement rules, etc. defines in § 2, para. 2,
                  point 1, a standstill period of 10 calendar days from the day after the date on
                  which the voluntary ex ante transparency notice is published in the Official
                  Journal of the European Union.</P>
